                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature approaches within 5 feet of the hatchet or more than 3 creatures enter area C10</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The furious shriek of Asethanna's rage resonates throughout the room, and all creatures within 25 feet of the hatchet must attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:25] save. The haunt then rolls initiative.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature feels as if the wrathful haunt is particularly enraged at them. The creature becomes frightened 2; their frightened condition doesn't decrease automatically as long as the haunt remains active, and the hatchet gains a +2 circumstance bonus to all wrathful hatchet Strikes it attempts against the creature.</p>"
